description: For sale: $135,000. Beautiful 5 acre piece of land with Pine River running through it and across the street from Cemetery Lake. Newer furnace, newer hot water heater, newer duct work, several newer windows, original hardwood floors, beautiful wood burning fireplace with stone hearth, walkout basement and views of the Pine River from your windows. An additional 5 acre property is for sale, that connects to this parcel. If you bought both, you could have a 10 acre home site.

description: For sale: $425,000. An unbelievable opportunity for your hunting sanctuary. Sellers have done all the hard work, now you can reap the rewards. 280 acre parcel with 2 bdrm/1 bath cabin and detached pole build. The cabin has a holding tank and drilled well. Great base camp with plenty of room to bring in extra campers/tents. This land has 11 various food plots, enclosed heated stands, planted shooting lanes, apple trees, and more! Scroll through all of the pictures for the various wildlife caught on the game cams - deer, bear, turkeys, grouse, geese and much more. A great mix of hardwood and evergreens, hay fields and rolling wooded areas with nice ridges, some lowlands and ponds. This could be your dream hunting getaway - less than 2 hours from the metro area, 10 minutes East of I-35 with tar road frontage.

description: For sale: $136,900. What a VIEW, what a GORGEOUS yard,  what a FANTASTIC setting! Kettle River Frontage AND Deeded Access to Long Lake on 6.5ac! The acreage is mostly mature oaks with wildlife galore. There is a great little beach when the river is lower. The home boast vaulted ceilings, 1 bedroom, lots of space in the loft, and a fireplace for the cooler summer evenings. New electric service panel with all new main floor electrical work. This is a nice property to take a walk through - please dress weather appropriate and wear mud boots!

For sale: $339,900. Beautiful & spacious home on 40 gorgeous acres in Willow River. Home built in 1998. You'll have 4 Bdrm on the main level and full Bath. Open concept with vaulted ceiling in the living rm area and walks out to a good size maintenance free deck. Nice size kitchen with lots of cabinets and counter space with butcher block center island. Dining / kitchen area has hardwood floor. Anderson windows throughout the house. Very convenient main floor laundry with 1/2 Bath plus storage. On the lower level you'll have big recreation / family  room with free standing wood fire place, another bedroom /craft room, office room, 3/4 Bath with shower and utility unfinished room. Very efficient forced air geothermal heating & cooling + in floor heat on LL with electric boiler. Beautiful yard with variety of fruit trees (apple, 3 cherry and 2 pear trees). 40x44 heated and nicely finished with tin butcher / meat processing shop with 16x40 cooler area, finished & heated 24x36 garage with dog kennel area on the outside, another 14x24 finished garage. Front field had corn last year and the back of the property has nice mature trees. Compliant septic system.
 
Home Warranty coverage will be included with acceptable offer. Feel free to call with any questions or if you'd like to set up your private showing.
